text: I don't believe in waiting for good
things to come I believe in going all
out to get them my philosophy is this
life is 10% of what happens to you and
90% what you make of it as a head of
solutions architecture at Amazon Web
Services for the Americas I see
firsthand the evolution and potential of
cloud computing
I believe cloud will change how the next
generation gets things done and I love
it growing up I loved learning new
languages and mathematics so my mother
signed me up for a coding class and I
haven't looked back since every day I
work with solution architects students
and builders from all backgrounds to me
inclusive teams are more productive and
are able to better serve our customers
I've seen and experienced how
representation and technology has
changed throughout my career things are
improving but there's still a lot we can
do to help build the future I want to
help those starting out in this industry
build better confidence to have them
work bravely towards their goals
